289
00:19:32,900 --> 00:19:35,200
Look, how's it?

290
00:19:35,200 --> 00:19:38,200
But we haven't asked if they even drink tea.

291
00:19:38,200 --> 00:19:40,700
If they don't, this can be served as a work of art.

