00:19:40,700 --> 00:19:43,100
The elderly usually like this. You don't understand.

293
00:19:43,100 --> 00:19:45,500
- All right, pack it up. 
 - Okay.

294
00:19:46,500 --> 00:19:49,900
You're staying there the whole weekend?

295
00:19:49,900 --> 00:19:52,400
I'll come back on Sunday.

296
00:19:54,400 --> 00:19:57,400
Then give me Xiao Tuo's apartment address.

297
00:19:57,400 --> 00:19:59,500
What do you want?

298
00:19:59,500 --> 00:20:01,600
I want to give him a housewarming gift.

299
00:20:01,600 --> 00:20:03,700
Okay. Thanks, Dad.

300
00:20:03,700 --> 00:20:06,200
- This won't fit. Just carry it by hand. 
 - I'll just carry it.

