00:20:11,000 --> 00:20:13,300
- More? 
 - Wait, there's more.

304
00:20:13,300 --> 00:20:17,300
Is she always this late? Or is it just with me?

305
00:20:17,300 --> 00:20:20,200
- Just wait a while. 
  - Coming.

