412
00:26:41,296 --> 00:26:44,596
Goji berry, lemon, and hawthorn, for refreshing your mind. Does it taste good?

413
00:26:44,596 --> 00:26:48,276
- Haven't tried it. 
 - Don't you drink water? Did you buy a drink?

414
00:26:48,276 --> 00:26:50,736
Drinking sweet stuff all the time isn't good for your brain.

415
00:26:50,736 --> 00:26:53,500
Why are you babbling at this age?

416
00:26:54,096 --> 00:26:57,576
Grandpa mentioned the chestnuts are good.
Let's go buy some for him.

417
00:26:57,576 --> 00:26:59,656
I know.

418
00:27:07,776 --> 00:27:11,516
- Isn't your dad coming back for dinner? 
 - I don't know.

419
00:27:11,516 --> 00:27:14,056
Just know how to play games.

420
00:27:14,056 --> 00:27:17,336
Wash your hands. Time for dinner.

421
00:27:17,336 --> 00:27:19,176
Xiao Ye.

422
00:27:23,551 --> 00:27:26,496
Dad, this is Xiao Que.

423
00:27:26,496 --> 00:27:28,656
Hello, Uncle. My name is An Zhique.

424
00:27:28,656 --> 00:27:30,656
Hello, Auntie.

425
00:27:30,656 --> 00:27:32,476
Hello.

426
00:27:32,476 --> 00:27:35,136
Dinner's ready. Go wash your hands.

427
00:27:35,136 --> 00:27:38,236
Okay, let's wash hands.

428
00:27:38,236 --> 00:27:39,956
The soup is here.

429
00:27:39,956 --> 00:27:42,080
Give it to me. I got it.

430
00:27:42,080 --> 00:27:43,860
Okay.

431
00:27:43,860 --> 00:27:46,216
Dad, you've made so many dishes.

432
00:27:46,216 --> 00:27:48,236
The cooking fumes are not good for your lungs.

433
00:27:48,236 --> 00:27:50,256
I have to show my granddaughter-in-law my cooking.

434
00:27:50,256 --> 00:27:52,056
I'm not doing it every day.

435
00:27:52,056 --> 00:27:55,196
- Since you're happy, go wash your hands. 
 - Okay, wash hands.

436
00:27:55,196 --> 00:27:56,896
Thank you, Grandpa.

437
00:27:56,896 --> 00:28:00,516
Now that you've become a regular, you can be a designer now?

438
00:28:01,216 --> 00:28:02,776
I'm still an assistant.

439
00:28:02,776 --> 00:28:05,256
But I'm ready to bid on the design project.

440
00:28:05,256 --> 00:28:06,816
I've made a proposal.

441
00:28:06,816 --> 00:28:08,536
Has it been approved?

442
00:28:08,536 --> 00:28:11,616
Not yet, but I'll keep doing it.

443
00:28:11,616 --> 00:28:13,736
Yours is a private company, right?

444
00:28:13,736 --> 00:28:16,056
Yes, but it's quite big.

445
00:28:16,056 --> 00:28:18,540
It has a shopping place and factories.

446
00:28:18,540 --> 00:28:20,845
Private companies are not stable.

447
00:28:20,845 --> 00:28:24,505
There are many variables in its development.

448
00:28:25,220 --> 00:28:27,236
Whether a company develops well or not

449
00:28:27,236 --> 00:28:31,716
