484
00:30:38,776 --> 00:30:41,016
Don't just keep talking.

485
00:30:41,016 --> 00:30:43,496
Don't leave tonight. Just stay at my place.

486
00:30:43,496 --> 00:30:46,056
My house is big. Just keep me company.

487
00:30:46,056 --> 00:30:48,036
Okay.

488
00:30:48,036 --> 00:30:50,016
Thank you.

489
00:30:50,016 --> 00:30:53,136
- Dad, I'll get you some soup. 
 - Okay.

490
00:31:04,636 --> 00:31:09,656
She has lost her mom, her dad drives a taxi,

491
00:31:09,656 --> 00:31:12,676
