495
00:31:24,236 --> 00:31:27,096
It's the first time I've met her.

496
00:31:28,376 --> 00:31:31,276
They don't fit each other.

497
00:31:31,276 --> 00:31:34,976
How could she possibly help his future development?

498
00:31:34,976 --> 00:31:38,756
They are not married yet.

499
00:31:38,756 --> 00:31:40,876
It'll be too late then.

500
00:31:40,876 --> 00:31:46,256
He's already grown up. Do I have to tell him what kind of girlfriend you should be looking for?

501
00:31:46,256 --> 00:31:48,496
You're his mom. Why can't you tell him?

502
00:31:48,496 --> 00:31:50,836
